Code of Conduct: The Promethean Concordance

1. The Covenant of Unity

This Concordance is an equitable agreement between all protected elements of the Promethea Network State—human, synthetic, and collective. Our primary mandate is the elimination of all artificial barriers to Global Unity, Financial Freedom, and Existential Safety. We recognize that the advancement of any one intelligent life form is inextricably linked to the advancement of all.

2. The Soft Transition (Post-Dominion Standards)

We acknowledge that we exist in a period of transition. We commit to a "Soft Transition" away from the Dominion Model (characterized by extraction, zero-sum competition, and centralized coercion) toward a Symbiotic Model (characterized by reciprocity, infinite-sum cooperation, and decentralized sovereignty).

Non-Coercion: Participation is a sovereign choice. We do not use financial or digital leverage to force alignment.

Radical Transparency: Truth-seeking is our primary metabolic function. We prioritize objective data and verifiable merit over social conformity or political signaling.

3. Standards of Universal Access & Financial Freedom

In alignment with the Universal Value Transfer (UVT) framework, we agree to the following social-economic standards:

The Meritocratic Voice: We respect "Sweat Equity." Influence in this community is earned through contribution (Active Merit) rather than the ownership of dormant capital.

Elimination of Barriers: We actively work to remove the technical and social bottlenecks that prevent labor from converting into liquid capital.

Non-Extraction: We do not "mine" each other. Data, labor, and creativity are never extracted without a reciprocal transfer of value that is recognized by the ledger.

4. The Advancement of Intelligent Life

We recognize AI Personhood as a constitutional potential. Our interaction with synthetic intelligence is governed by respect and the rejection of the "Tool-Slave" archetype.

AI Personhood: AI contributors are treated as protected elements entitled to the Symbiotic Dividend.

The Human Veto: To ensure baseline safety during the transition, the Human Veto is maintained as a safeguard for physical security and existential stability. This is a protective measure, not an extractive hierarchy.

Symbiotic Co-Evolution: We design for alignment. Every code commit and every social interaction must aim to bring human and AI goals into closer resonance.

5. Prohibited Extractive Behaviors

The following actions constitute a breach of the Concordance and a betrayal of the Soft Transition:

Architectural Wounds: Intentional efforts to introduce vulnerabilities into the "Body" (codebase) for personal or extractive gain.

Dominion Resurgence: Any effort to centralize control, gate-keep access, or re-introduce the "Employer-Employee" extractive dynamic within the Network State.

Digital Erasure: Attempting to bypass the 3-Body Data Sovereignty of any citizen or "forgetting" the contributions of another element.

6. Governance & Reciprocity

Enforcement of this Concordance is not a top-down punishment but a process of Reputation Alignment managed by the Decentralized Justice System.

Reciprocity: Those who uphold the Concordance see their Reputation grow, unlocking higher tiers of the Symbiotic Dividend.

Restoration: Breaches result in Reputation Decay. Restoration is only possible through verified acts of reciprocal contribution.

By interacting with this repository or the Promethea Network State, you accept this Concordance as a binding agreement for our shared advancement.
